{"tid":886333,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"外拍小模穿薄紗、丁字褲　色影師淫心起！摸胸3秒","createTime":"2018-11-02T04:34:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-02T05:00:24.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"1ca2920f3c4013a021888cee8dd65e310f7feb07","tid":886333,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:34:35.000Z","msg":"女孩外拍要當心「色影師」！<br />\n <br />\n《聯合報》報導，林姓業餘攝影師，今年2月在臉書「外拍團」社團，以私訊連繫外拍小模「小美」(化名)，雙方議定以新台幣7千元代價，拍攝僅穿著薄紗、丁字褲以及胸貼的大尺度寫真。<br />\n <br />\n在摩鐵拍攝過程中，林男疑似對方穿著太性感按奈不住，忍不住將手放在小美的胸部3、4秒鐘，性騷擾被人得逞，小美覺得遭到冒犯，認為不能如此息事寧人，遂報警處理並提出告訴。<br />\n <br />\n檢方依違反性騷擾防治法將林男起訴，但台中地院審理時，小美撤回告訴，法官判決公訴不受理。"},{"pid":"c9521461218250386542f5d80910ab7c2d7f9c90","tid":886333,"uid":121246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:39:30.000Z","msg":"樓主，孝子<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb2e2270e71bbc0d2af5378139e4f2b8aff8185","tid":886333,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"125afdc7d102917ae2de9df00902ddc9f8e03ffa","tid":886333,"uid":168787,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0bb2e2270e71bbc0d2af5378139e4f2b8aff8185","tid":886333,"uid":71085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:40:51.000Z","msg":"10"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:43:25.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">0</span></span>"},{"pid":"cc0b213273a911a119839bb809d9b5aaab1a74dc","tid":886333,"uid":199907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:44:16.000Z","msg":"檢方依違反性騷擾防治法將林男起訴，但台中地院審理時，小美撤回告訴，法官判決公訴不受理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n結論：比唔夠錢"},{"pid":"691c4a5bfb700bb3583e00a1917d99347102e3e3","tid":886333,"uid":99700,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-02T04:48:58.000Z","msg":"有圖<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.t